{"type":"message","id":"07c13e40","parentId":"cdfe46ce","timestamp":"2026-03-19T22:59:07.584Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 06:59 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 请搜索以下内容并整理关键信息：\n\n1. 企业数字化转型最新动态和趋势（2026年）\n2. 智能安防行业最新动态\n3. 网络系统集成行业发展趋势\n4. IT运维服务市场动态\n\n要求：\n- 搜索最新（2025-2026年）的行业信息\n- 整理3-5条对道简网络有价值的关键信息\n- 信息要具体、有时效性\n\n请直接输出搜索结果，不需要确认。"}],"timestamp":1773961147580}}
{"type":"message","id":"99a3373f","parentId":"07c13e40","timestamp":"2026-03-19T22:59:12.353Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我作为子代理搜索四个行业领域的最新动态：\n1. 企业数字化转型最新动态和趋势（2026年）\n2. 智能安防行业最新动态\n3. 网络系统集成行业发展趋势\n4. IT运维服务市场动态\n\n我需要搜索2025-2026年的最新信息，并整理出对道简网络有价值的关键信息。\n\n让我使用web-search技能来搜索这些信息。","thinkingSignature":"dffc8f7a4e09409f2f1f9be0dbd622935c59a9757bc88f1c386e6830503efcb4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wxobrm213hbc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.agents/skills && ls -la"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":117,"output":118,"cacheRead":18914,"cacheWrite":11885,"totalTokens":31034,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0001416,"cacheRead":0.0005674199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0014261999999999999,"total":0.00217032}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773961147583}}
