{"type":"message","id":"a1fdfb8a","parentId":"6d7a42b3","timestamp":"2026-03-19T22:59:29.062Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vfg9d87pyp2x_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"total 36\ndrwxr-xr-x  9 gem gem 4096 Mar 18 22:41 .\ndrwx------ 23 gem gem 4096 Mar 19 14:50 ..\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 gem gem 4096 Mar 12 13:08 miaoda-doc-parse\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 gem gem 4096 Mar 12 13:08 miaoda-image-understanding\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 gem gem 4096 Mar 12 13:08 miaoda-speech-to-text\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 gem gem 4096 Mar 12 13:08 miaoda-text-gen-image\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 gem gem 4096 Mar 12 13:08 miaoda-web-fetch\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 gem gem 4096 Mar 12 13:08 miaoda-web-search\ndrwxr-xr-x  3 gem gem 4096 Mar 18 22:41 weda-connector"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"total 36\ndrwxr-xr-x  9 gem gem 4096 Mar 18 22:41 .\ndrwx------ 23 gem gem 4096 Mar 19 14:50 ..\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 gem gem 4096 Mar 12 13:08 miaoda-doc-parse\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 gem gem 4096 Mar 12 13:08 miaoda-image-understanding\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 gem gem 4096 Mar 12 13:08 miaoda-speech-to-text\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 gem gem 4096 Mar 12 13:08 miaoda-text-gen-image\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 gem gem 4096 Mar 12 13:08 miaoda-web-fetch\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 gem gem 4096 Mar 12 13:08 miaoda-web-search\ndrwxr-xr-x  3 gem gem 4096 Mar 18 22:41 weda-connector","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773961169058}}
{"type":"message","id":"17c9d95d","parentId":"a1fdfb8a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T22:59:32.074Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我查看miaoda-web-search技能。","thinkingSignature":"7ba5dbf7bd714fe8580e4fa3ec2c99cb9a9bb8a595e29d022e36eb47ef8e943c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l25ctdevblos_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":31400,"output":48,"cacheRead":30641,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62089,"cost":{"input":0.00942,"output":0.0000576,"cacheRead":0.0009192299999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01039683}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773961169061}}
{"type":"message","id":"065bce99","parentId":"17c9d95d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T22:59:32.081Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_l25ctdevblos_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773961172077}}
